The N7 pass near Citrusdal has been closed after a truck rolled down the mountain slope. CAPE TOWN - The N7 pass near Citrusdal has been closed after a truck rolled down the mountain slope.Emergency services are currently attempting to assist the driver who is still trapped inside.Western Cape Traffic chief Kenny Africa says it is unclear how long the operation may take. Currently we have a situation in Citrusdal, where a truck went down the mountain. The driver is still trapped inside the truck. (Edited by Zamangwane Shange)